<h1>Nyhedsgruppen dk.edb.internet.webdesign.serverside.asp</h1><p>Gruppen er til spørgsmål/diskussion af de problemer der er ved at fremstille websider ved brug af Active Server Pages.</p><hr /><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3Ca4tq6f%24i7v%241%40newsreader%2Emailgate%2Eorg%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign.serverside.asp</a></div>

<!-- FreeFind End No Index -->

<ul class='messageheaderlist'><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Afsender:</span></strong> Lars&nbsp;Hoffmann&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href='mailto:lars@intercambiodvd.com'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon.newsgroups.mail.gif' alt='lars@intercambiodvd.com' /></a></li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Organisation:</span></strong> Mailgate.ORG Server - http://www.Mailgate.ORG</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Dato:</span></strong> 19. februar 2002 kl. 17:16</li><li class='messageheaderlist'><strong class='diff'><span class='messageheader'>Emne:</span></strong> <strong>RE: form submission via email + db insertion</strong></li></ul>

<p><span class='normal'>Quinn &lt;<a href='http://sstian@online.no'>sstian@online.no</a>> escribi&#243; en el mensaje de noticias </span><br /><span class='normal'><a href='http://TGtc8.8681$HL2.199291@news2.ulv.nextra.no'>TGtc8.8681$HL2.199291@news2.ulv.nextra.no</a>... </span><br /><span class='citat'>> I have a user thats really bugging me in my open forum on my website, </span><br /><span class='normal'>and I </span><br /><span class='citat'>> would like to see if I could get his e-mail-address so that I can tell </span><br /><span class='normal'>him </span><br /><span class='citat'>> that I know who he is and that he should stop bugging me. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>I could talk for hours about what a really bad idea this is, but just </span><br /><span class='normal'>take the following into consideration: </span><br /><span class='normal'>1) he might not use his personal computer to bother you, and it is </span><br /><span class='normal'>possible that you get the email of somebody who has nothing to do with </span><br /><span class='normal'>it. </span><br /><span class='normal'>2) With most email programs you can simply answer 'NO' whenever a </span><br /><span class='normal'>homepage tries to send an email, any person who is aware of beeing </span><br /><span class='normal'>annoying would simply click no to sending a form that way </span><br /><span class='normal'>3) action=&quot;mailto...&quot; has mayor compatibility issues, and thus you might </span><br /><span class='normal'>end up bothering one of your innocent users. </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> The tricky part is that as this is an open discussion group I want to </span><br /><span class='normal'>keep </span><br /><span class='citat'>> his submissions to the forum as well, which means that I have to </span><br /><span class='normal'>perform two </span><br /><span class='citat'>> tasks: </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> 1. form submission via mail </span><br /><span class='citat'>> 2. insertion to database with ASP. (just like normal on the discussion </span><br /><span class='citat'>> group). </span><br /><span class='citat'>> </span><br /><span class='citat'>> Any ideas on this one? </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'>Yeah sure, its not difficult at all, but I wont help you either. The </span><br /><span class='normal'>thing to do it is: Log his IP, use <a href='http://www.geektools.com'>www.geektools.com</a> to find his ISP, </span><br /><span class='normal'>and write a complaint to them. </span><br /><span class='normal'>Best regards </span><br /><span class='normal'>Lars Hoffmann </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'> </span><br /><span class='normal'></span><br /></p><hr /><ul class='newslist'><li class='newslist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?messageid=%3CTGtc8%2E8681%24HL2%2E199291%40news2%2Eulv%2Enextra%2Eno%3E' title='form submission via email + db insertion'>form submission via email + db insertion</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(19-02-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Quinn)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?messageid=%3Ca4tq6f%24i7v%241%40newsreader%2Emailgate%2Eorg%3E' title='RE: form submission via email + db insertion'>RE: form submission via email + db insertion</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(19-02-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Lars&nbsp;Hoffmann)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?messageid=%3CxIuc8%2E6539%24%25m1%2E135589%40news4%2Eulv%2Enextra%2Eno%3E' title='Re: form submission via email + db insertion'>Re: form submission via email + db insertion</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(19-02-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Quinn)</small><ul class='relist'><li class='relist'><a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?messageid=%3Ca4tuec%24l3s%241%40newsreader%2Emailgate%2Eorg%3E' title='RE: form submission via email + db insertion'>RE: form submission via email + db insertion</a>&nbsp;<small class='newslist'>(19-02-02&nbsp;-&nbsp;Lars&nbsp;Hoffmann)</small></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><div class='newsbox'><img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_reply.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?mode=form&amp;ReplyID=%3Ca4tq6f%24i7v%241%40newsreader%2Emailgate%2Eorg%3E'>Svar på dette indlæg</a>&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_new.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp?mode=form'>Skriv et nyt indlæg</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src='/site/graphics/icons/icon_list.gif' alt=' | ' />&nbsp;<a href='/nyhedsgrupper/dk_edb_internet_webdesign_serverside_asp/Default.asp'>dk.edb.internet.webdesign.serverside.asp</a></div><dl><dt></dt><dd></dd></dl>



